McMahon Says Thornburg Likes Telecommunications Stocks

-- B y  
-- 
2011-09-14T20:56:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-14/mcmahon-says-thornburg-likes-telecommunications-stocks-video.html
Brian McMahon, chief executive 
officer of Thornburg  Investment Management , talks about his 
investment strategy and some of his stock picks including TDC 
A/S, Royal KPN NV,  China Mobile Ltd. (941)  and Telstra Corp.  He speaks with Lisa Murphy and  Matt Miller  on Bloomberg 
Television's "Street Smart." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 04:28
 